Copy folders with the needed themes to `~/.themes` for the current user only. Or to `/usr/share/themes` for all users (requires sudo).
Copy folders with icons and cursors to `~/.icons`.
Then switch them in Tweaks.


To install the grub themes, follow the instructions inside the `grub` subfolder.


Themes:

Ultimate dark: https://www.pling.com/p/1246387/
Cameo Ubuntu: https://www.pling.com/p/1390642/
Manjarin: https://www.pling.com/p/1231824/


Icons: 

Ultimate: https://www.pling.com/p/1218961/


Cursors:

Volantes: https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1356095/
